            <title>[OAK-3136] High memory usage of SegmentDataStoreBlobGCTest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-3136</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Today my oak-core build stalled at SegmentDataStoreBlobGCTest running nearly OOM. The heap dump showed a SegmentTracker, which consumed 256MB of memory. This is the default cache size for the Cache inside the SegmentTracker. For this test, the cache size should be reduced.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
